The paper discusses the use of neural networks for reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the drawbacks of using neural networks for this task and proposes modifications to improve stability, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the use of reinforcement learning in control systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper proposes modifications to improve the performance of deep Q-networks, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) as deep Q-networks are commonly used in robotics applications.
